Subject: US v. Maxwell, 20 Cr. 330 (AJN) - Letter from MDC Legal Counsel 
Date: Thu, 29 Apr 2021 22:38:12 +0000 
Attachments: Ltr to Hon Nathan_04.29.21_--.pdf 
Good afternoon, 
Attached is a letter from MDC legal counsel in response to the Court's April 29, 2021 Order (Dkt. 255). Because the MDC 
is not a party to this case, this letter has not been filed on ECF, but the Government has no objection to the public 
docketing of this letter. 
Respectfully, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
United States Attorney's Office 
Southern District of New York 
One St. Plaza 
New York, New York 10007 
Tel:
